room_title: Escape room "Lost Cabin" by 601 Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
room_description: These backwoods hold a secret. You know how the horror movies go. You know that staying a night in this cabin is a horrible idea. But sometimes you have to face the fear head on if you want to know the truth. Ancient magic books, pleas for help by the past victims and an evil lurking in the shadows... Are you brave enough to enter, and can you find a way to escape?
